p: Proximate composition of A.trifoliatus leaf samples including moisture, crude protein, total fat, total carbohydrate, dietary fiber, ash; as well as, energy were found to be 74.62±0.38, 5.01±0.05, 0.95±0.04, 16.47±0.40, 8.54±0.06, 2.95±0.04 g/100 g sample respectively, and energy was found to be 94.48±1.30 kcal/100 g sample.
